     1→# Configuration
     3→This section details the configuration options available in the ***book.toml***:
     4→- **[General]** configuration including the `book`, `rust`, `build` sections
     5→- **[Preprocessor]** configuration for default and custom book preprocessors
     6→- **[Renderer]** configuration for the HTML, Markdown and custom renderers
     7→- **[Environment Variable]** configuration for overriding configuration options in your environment
